---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About Marc Evans | US Gravity';
const description = 'Stratospheric thinking. Ground-level execution. Meet Marc Evans — the Virtual CIO and IT consulting expert behind Gravity Limited. Based in Denver, CO, serving companies across the USA.';
const permalink = `${Astro.site.href}about`;
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} permalink={permalink} current="about">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="about-header">
      <div class="about-text-lead">
        <p class="eyebrow">Stratospheric Thinking. Ground-Level Execution.</p>
        <h1>Your Technology Has Been in Freefall. Let's Change That.</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-body">
      <figure class="about-image">
        <div class="portrait-placeholder" aria-label="Marc Evans, Founder of Gravity Limited">
          <div class="portrait-inner">
            <span class="portrait-initials">ME</span>
            <p class="portrait-name">Marc Evans</p>
            <p class="portrait-title">Founder & Virtual CIO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </figure>

      <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Hi, I'm Marc Evans.</h2>

        <p>
          I founded Gravity Limited on a simple premise: every company — regardless of size — deserves executive-level IT leadership. Most small and mid-size businesses can't justify the cost of a full-time Chief Information Officer. But they absolutely need that thinking, that experience, and that strategic gravity pulling their technology decisions in the right direction.
        </p>

        <p>
          That's where I come in.
        </p>

        <p>
          Based in Denver, Colorado, I work with companies throughout the United States as a Virtual CIO and IT consulting partner. I embed alongside your leadership team to understand your business goals first — and then build the technology strategy, leadership structure, and project roadmap to get you there.
        </p>

        <h2>What I Actually Do</h2>

        <p>
          Think of me as the IT leader your company needs, without the overhead of a full-time executive hire. Some of my clients need help building their IT function from scratch. Others have a team in place but lack strategic direction at the top. And some just need a trusted expert to lead a critical project or navigate a compliance initiative.
        </p>

        <p>
          Whether you need me to <strong>improve your IT team</strong>, <strong>build your IT team</strong>, or <strong>accent it with senior-level expertise</strong> — I scale to fit what you actually need, not what looks good on a contract.
        </p>

        <h2>Industries I Know Well</h2>

        <p>
          Over the course of my career, I've built deep experience in industries where technology failures aren't just costly — they're consequential. I've worked in and alongside companies in Energy, Mining and Prospecting, Power Generation, Industrial and BioMedical Manufacturing, and Logistics. These are environments where uptime matters, compliance is non-negotiable, and the margin for error is thin.
        </p>

        <p>
          That said, I've helped companies outside these sectors too. If your business is hitting a wall — scaling too fast, struggling with compliance, inheriting bad infrastructure, or simply lacking IT leadership — I can likely help.
        </p>

        <h2>Why "Gravity"?</h2>

        <p>
          Gravity is the force that gives things structure and keeps systems in orbit. Without it, things drift. In business, that drift looks like misaligned technology, reactive IT decisions, siloed teams, and missed opportunities.
        </p>

        <p>
          The tagline — <em>Stratospheric thinking. Ground-level execution.</em> — is how I work. I bring the wide-angle, long-range perspective of an experienced technology executive, then roll up my sleeves and make it real inside your organization. No ivory tower strategy decks that gather dust. No junior consultants handed the work after the pitch. Just Marc, doing the thinking and the doing.
        </p>

        <div class="about-cta">
          <p>Ready to have a real conversation about your IT situation?</p>
          <a href="mailto:usgravity.ethically151@passfwd.com" class="btn btn-primary">Reach Out to Marc</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-header {
    margin: 2em 0 2.5em;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.85em;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.4em;
  }

  .about-text-lead h1 {
    font-size: 2.2em;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.25;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ── Layout ── */
  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3em;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-image {
    flex: 0 0 260px;
    margin: 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 2em;
  }

  .about-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  /* ── Portrait Placeholder ── */
  /* Replace this block with an <img> tag when a photo is available */
  .portrait-placeholder {
    width: 240px;
    height: 300px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--text-link, #0066cc) 0%, #003880 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .portrait-inner {
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .portrait-initials {
    display: block;
    font-size: 3em;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.4em;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .portrait-name {
    font-size: 1em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.2em;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .portrait-title {
    font-size: 0.8em;
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ── Content ── */
  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.4em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 1.8em 0 0.5em;
  }

  .about-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.05em;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .about-content strong {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .about-cta {
    margin-top: 2.5em;
    padding: 2em;
    background: var(--background-body-alt, #f6f8fc);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-cta p {
    font-size: 1.1em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75em 1.75em;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--text-link);
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .about-body {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-image {
      position: static;
      flex: none;
    }

    .about-text-lead h1 {
      font-size: 1.7em;
    }
  }
</style>
